# PHASE 16: ENHANCEMENT SYSTEM

## Strategic Context

**The Input Motivation Loop:**
```
User creates note/meeting
         ‚îÇ
         ‚ñº
Gets immediate utility (clean output) ‚Üê GRANOLA PARITY
         ‚îÇ
         ‚ñº
Sees Inscript Context (patterns, history) ‚Üê "WHOA" MOMENT
         ‚îÇ
         ‚ñº
Inputs more data ‚Üê BEHAVIOR CHANGE
         ‚îÇ
         ‚ñº
Memory system enriches ‚Üê COMPOUNDING VALUE
         ‚îÇ
         ‚ñº
User becomes dependent on Inscript Context ‚Üê MOAT
```

**Core Principle:** Utility gets users in the door. Context keeps them building.

